Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:18.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:21.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:26.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have to take back that "Let's pretend nothing happened".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:31.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I still like you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:33.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:43.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I like who I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:56.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:07.23,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(1028,770)\3c&H0A0909&\q2\pos(645,399)}A Confrontation with the Ex-Girlfriend?!\NThe Great Chest Baring Plan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:11.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:12.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been cut off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty lame, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:18.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, Umibouzu's wife, couldn't you have done better?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:21.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, here's another picture of you looking lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:23.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What? There are more?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:26.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:28.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:31.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I? I took it using my own camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:34.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No good will come of you having that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:37.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I could print out a few more copies and put them up in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you treat the guy you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:45.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to say stuff like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault, no matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:50.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm definitely gonna print more copies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:54.35,lovely - TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,In Japan, small packets of tissues are commonly handed out for free as a method of advertising.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:54.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make a hundred copies and hand them out with tissues in front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:55.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I really will hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:57.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, if you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The data is still stored in my camera, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:01.15,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,They're back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:02.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A little too normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:04.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:08.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani knows my biggest weakness now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:09.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is making me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:14.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to make Otani-kun regret rejecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:18.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, don't make that ugly face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Think. Why did he reject you in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:27.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because he thinks of you as his comedy partner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:29.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:32.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just keep doing comedy with him like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your seductiveness! Seductiveness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:34.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Seductiveness"{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:37.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly, bare your chest completely and move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:38.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:39.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do a lap of the station area!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:40.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean show that kind of attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:50.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is a {\i1}"chest baring attitude"{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:57.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:02.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A year sure goes by quickly, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you an old woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:14.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...last Christmas, he blew off his ex-girlfriend and kept me company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:16.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure was cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:20.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What was your relationship with Kanzaki-san like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:25.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It would bother anyone in my position.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:29.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was normal. Normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:30.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:31.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:36.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well you guys weren't ever a comedy duo, were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl Otani went out with...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl he liked...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:53.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become the girl that Otani likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:01.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I give my darling for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiharu-chan, what are you going to give Suzuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, last year I gave him a sweater...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:14.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:20.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa, you don't have any plans for Christmas this year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ask Otani-kun out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him you want to spend Christmas eve together, just the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:26.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:28.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He rejected me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could say something so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:34.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He already knows you like him, and nothing could be more embarrassing than that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:38.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I still like you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm remembering pointless things again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:44.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing! I'm so embarrassed I could die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:45.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I should never have told him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:46.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:47.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine, you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:51.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is naturally embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:54.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone loves whilst fighting against embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:57.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get together with Nakao-chi, Nobu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:58.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:04.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a winter's day, when the rain was cold as snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:12.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a former gang leader, Nakao-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:16.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he put twenty delinquents from another school in the hospital all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my! How scary!
