Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:40.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I live in an apartment, so I can't take you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:46.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like milk, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:53.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And then one day, I was picked on by some delinquents,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:56.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,and the leader of their gang turned out to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:57.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:06:59.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I put a love letter in his locker...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:00.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:01.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding. just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:04.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,In our last year of middle school, we attended the same cram school and became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:05.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Cram school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:10.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I said to him, {\i1}"if only I had a boyfriend like you, Nakao-kun..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:13.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And he said, {\i1}"If only I had a girlfriend like you, Nobu-chan..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:14.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And then it was like, {\i1}"So why don't we go out?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no drama involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:19.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good thing. I've had enough of drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:24.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The person you like likes you back. That's pretty impressive in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost a miracle, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:27.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:29.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Chiharu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:29.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:34.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You got your miracle easily enough, and things have gone well with Suzuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:39.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You two should be more thankful to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It-It-It's just me that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What the hell...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:47.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Alcohol?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine, Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't  say that he didn't like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:53.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Risa. Just do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:56.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't bare my chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:00.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! No one told you to do it literally!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant mentally bare your chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Mentally bare my chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:05.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:08.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Reveal the inner breasts that lie deep within your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:10.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine aren't as big as yours, Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:11.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with size.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bare them! Go on! Bare them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:14.31,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should lower your voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:17.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it if you really want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:19.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're cute too, Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:21.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:26.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just use a bit of charm and Otani-kun will be done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm All-Kyojin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:31.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're tall like a model. What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:33.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:37.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:42.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Believe in miracles"{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:58.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I want Otani to fall in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:02.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:04.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The great Christmas plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:09.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll need to find a Christmas present for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:10.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll reveal my chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:12.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:21.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...are you doing anything for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:28.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you mean, {\i1}"disgusting"{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I am, desperately trying to bare my chest to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:36.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:40.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... anyway... are you free for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:41.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,For Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:42.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:47.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it matter? So you're doing something for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:54.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. My middle school's basketball club is getting together for a Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:10:01.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's like the one that Kanzaki-san invited you to last year, but you didn't go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah. You remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:05.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:09.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then Kanzaki-san will be going too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the manager, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:21.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pull that face! It seriously pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:28.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, there's nothing going on between me and that girl, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"That girl"{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:31.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're calling her {\i1}"that girl?"{\i0} now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:35.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my! Have you heard, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:37.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He just said {\i1}"There's nothing going on between me and that girl"{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to be able to say something like that myself. How cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:40.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:42.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:47.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, he hung out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I did make plans with you first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was because of the Umibouzu concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:00.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he considered me more important than his ex-girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:04.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that. I knew it, but I was still happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:10.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Without an Umibouzu ticket, I'm just an All-Kyojin to be rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:15.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, Go have a merry Christmas with that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:18.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, when you just happen to get back together,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:20.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,this rejected All-Kyojin will simply stand by silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:27.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:30.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come along? To the Christmas party, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:36.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? I don't have anything to do with your middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:43.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a party, but we'll be playing a bit of basketball too, so the more the merrier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nakao couple are coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:47.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:48.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:51.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can spend Christmas Eve alone together,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,then we can go to the party on Christmas day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:55.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh. That's okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:55.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:56.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:04.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they already ordered a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:16.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna eat it in the gym? Won't we get in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:18.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:21.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the great Christmas plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:23.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bare your chest, and more forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:27.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:31.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Whether it's an ex-girlfriend or whatever, bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:36.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Using my chest baring power I'll make Otani fall for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:40.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:43.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Otani-senpai and Nakao-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:44.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani-sempai is as short as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll smack you for that, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The ex-girlfriend isn't here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani-sempai, I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:57.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager Kanzaki couldn't make it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:03.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you two back together yet or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:07.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you guys! I told you there's nothing going on between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:11.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, don't look so obviously happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:14.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:17.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani's new girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:20.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, n-no. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:24.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just an amazon who's in the same class as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's not your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't look like she would be, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:33.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:35.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have phrased that better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:37.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a sense of kindness or compassion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I said anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:42.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't say anything right, you microbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't bare your chest. You bared your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:50.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how is this a Christmas party?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:55.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently we'll be having a cake later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:56.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:58.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:02.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The sweaty look doesn't suit you at all, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you guys join in too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:06.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't bring my sneakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't play basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So why couldn't Kanzaki make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She said something came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:19.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And we were going to go to all that effort to get her and Otani back together too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But doesn't she have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:24.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We could have just passed that off as a thing of the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:31.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani liked Kanzaki-san a lot, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:36.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like he died after they broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It really damaged him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:41.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was difficult to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I never heard about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:46.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that it would bother Koizumi-san if I mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:53.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:57.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what were Otani and Kanzaki-san like as a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What were they like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:03.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Otani was head over heels in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:06.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Before they started going out, he'd get incredibly nervous and could barely speak around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:12.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So we thought it would be funny to lock the two of them in the storeroom together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:19.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,After they got out, they started going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:23.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what happened in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what could have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:36.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's payback for before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And you two, how long are you planning on drawing out that break for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:41.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Gossiping again, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We were not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:44.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:50.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of someone he likes, he gets so nervous he can barely speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:55.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:02.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:05.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What about your chest?! Your chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:07.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.39,0:16:12.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that girl doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:15.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Otani, are you interested in that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:16.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:21.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she doesn't seem your type at all, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:22.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...she's a fun girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:26.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:30.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare to find a girl as fun as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:33.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you kinda like her then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:38.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the chest! Reconsider, Risa! Reconsider!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:43.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. You bring Otani-kun and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:55.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll get everyone to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:17:01.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa, we'll get yelled at if we eat cake in here, so we're going to eat outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:02.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:06.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, before that, could you put this ball back in the storeroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go, just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:16.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. Toss it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, was that a click just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:34.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, this is for real, You got mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:41.12,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord0\fs19\fay-0.08\c&H595253&\frz337\fnNarkisim\pos(375,73)}\h Nobu-chan\N\N\N\N\N\h              Bare your chest{\fs18}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fs19}We'll come and open the door\N later. Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:38.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bare your chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:40.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come and open the door later. Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:46.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:48.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:50.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:52.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:55.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me to bare my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:58.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't expose such a dangerous area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:00.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. They got us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:03.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:04.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Oh well"{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:06.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:12.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...when you and Kanzaki-san were locked in the storeroom, you weren't this calm, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:20.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-H-How do you know about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:22.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:24.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you?! I'll kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:26.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you two do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:31.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you two do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:36.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,In this dark room, all alone with Kanzaki-san, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:39.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all, you idiot! We just talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering you were so nervous you couldn't even talk straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,what could you two have talked about all alone together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You even know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:48.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, those guys are gonna pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:56.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it was something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So you really liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:10.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you, that was in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:11.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:13.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:24.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have been crying a lot lately, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think is to blame for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:27.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:30.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so genuinely surprised. Who else could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I guess that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:36.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracles can't happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:45.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A Christmas present.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:52.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought it on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:55.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless keeping it, so I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:03.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're gloves! I've been wanting some.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:04.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:08.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't get anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:09.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:11.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I was expecting anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:13.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:22.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like me that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:30.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why are you saying that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:31.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:35.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"But"{\i0} nothing! Stop blabbering pointless things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:40.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hurry up and open the door, Nobu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:47.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:51.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:55.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Find something funny, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It is funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:04.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:07.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is wrong with you?! Maybe you really do have a bad personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:09.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny, funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:12.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:24.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Christmas, so it'd be nice if a miracle happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:22.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki broke up with her boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:23.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:25.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani is going to be swept off his feet by his ex-girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:27.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're overdoing it with the adrenaline.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.85,0:23:29.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely Complex~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:32.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Next: Complete Despair! A Love Revival with the Ex?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:33.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to watch!
